### 회원가입
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/signup HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "tester@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234!"
}

###

### 회원가입 - 이메일 중복
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/signup HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "tester@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234!"
}

###

### 로그인 - 성공
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "tester@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234!"
}

###

### 로그인 - 비밀번호 오류
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "tester@example.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###

### 로그인 - 존재하지 않는 이메일
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "notexist@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234!"
}

###

### 현재 로그인 사용자 조회
GET http://localhost:4000/api/auth/me HTTP/1.1

###

### 로그아웃
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/logout HTTP/1.1
